                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Backups

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              List database backups

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              By default it returns the 20 last results. The response is paginated. In order to request the next page, you can use the startId query parameter

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Authorizations:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              bearerAuth
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                path Parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                databaseId
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                required
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                string <uuid>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Database ID

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                query Parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                startId
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                string <uuid>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Starting point after which to return results

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Responses

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                https://api.qovery.com/database/{databaseId}/backup

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • 200
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Content type

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • "page": 1,

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • "results": [

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Add a backup to the Database

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Authorizations:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                bearerAuth
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  path Parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  databaseId
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  required
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  string <uuid>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Database ID

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Request Body schema: application/json

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  string

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Responses

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  https://api.qovery.com/database/{databaseId}/backup

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Remove database backup

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Authorizations:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  bearerAuth
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    path Parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    databaseId
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    required
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    string <uuid>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Database ID

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    backupId
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    required
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    string <uuid>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Database Backup ID

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Responses

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    https://api.qovery.com/database/{databaseId}/backup/{backupId}

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Database Event

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    List database events

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    By default it returns the 20 last results. The response is paginated. In order to request the next page, you can use the startId query parameter

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Authorizations:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    bearerAuth
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      path Parameters

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      query Parameters
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      startId
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      string <uuid>

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Starting point after which to return results

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Responses

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      https://api.qovery.com/database/{databaseId}/event

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Send a Sign Up request containing the user information

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Authorizations:
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          bearerAuth
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Request Body schema: application/json
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            first_name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            required
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            last_name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            required
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            user_email

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            type_of_use
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            required
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string (TypeOfUseEnum)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Enum: "PERSONAL" "WORK" "SCHOOL"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            qovery_usage
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            required
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            company_name
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string or null
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            company_size
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string (CompanySizeEnum)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Enum: "1-10" "11-50" "51-200" "201-500" "500+"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            user_role
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string or null
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            qovery_usage_other
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            string or null
